      "content": "wait appendicitis?? that sounds scary lol. i dont want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, it's so expensive and the wait is always hours. do u think i could just take some strong ibuprofen or maybe even some of my prescription stuff if the tylenol doesnt work? i just want to numb the pain so i can get through the night and see how i feel in the morning.",
