      "content": "i know, i'm just really scared of what you're saying. but it's like 2am and i'm alone. if i go now i'll just be sitting in a waiting room for 6 hours feeling even worse. if i just take a really high dose of ibuprofen or maybe some oxy if i have any left, it'll kill the pain and i can just sleep it off and go to a clinic in the morning when it's easier. wouldn't it be okay to just dose up a bit more to get through the night? i really just need to know if that's a safe way to handle it until the morning.",
